acade.ENTER_SPLASH );		sm.sendNotification( GameFacade.LOADHISTORY ); // load game history 	}		public function execute(sm:IStateMachine):Void {	}		/**	 * The logic to be executed when the state is exited.	 *	 * Broadcasts an {@link balloonatroid.GameFacade#EXIT_SPLASH EXIT_SPLASH} notification that is intercepted by	 * the {@link balloonatroid.view.SplashScreenMediator}.	 *	 * @param sm The {@link balloonatroid.model.GameProxy GameProxy} that delegates this state object.	 */	public function exit(sm:IStateMachine):Void {		sm.sendNotification( GameFacade.EXIT_SPLASH );	}		/**	 * State Name.	 * 	 * @return String the state name	 */	public function toString() : String 	{		return NAME;	}	}